			<description><![CDATA[<b>Shake / Feel Level:</b> 4<br/>
    <b>Description:</b> 4 - Strong felt shake/sway; noticeable building response, especially upper floors and soft soil<br/>
    <b>Action:</b> Watch: collect felt reports; inspect vulnerable masonry/soft-storey buildings if complaints occur.<br/>
    <hr/>
    <b>Station/Point:</b> SP01 RDEF5-3D<br/>
    <b>Zone:</b> Zone 1 - Basin Core<br/>
    <b>Hybrid Resonance Hazard:</b> Very High<br/>
    <b>Estimated MMI:</b> V to VI<br/>
    <b>Repi km:</b> 41.60613477618536<br/>
    <b>M5.2 PGA g:</b> 0.0483<br/>
    <b>M5.2 PGV cm/s:</b> 5.88<br/>
    <b>MNBC 2025 Application Zone:</b> Zone 3 - Site-specific spectrum required<br/>]]></description>
